```

### Required test cases

1. `addToQueue appends item with unique id and content` ‚Äî add two items, verify queue length is 2, each has a unique `id`, `content` matches, and `createdAt` is a number.
2. `addToQueue with empty string is rejected` ‚Äî call `addToQueue('')`, verify queue length remains 0.
3. `updateQueueItem modifies content at index, preserves id` ‚Äî add item, capture its id, update content, verify id unchanged and content updated.
4. `removeFromQueue removes item and adjusts editingIndex` ‚Äî add 3 items, start editing index 2, remove index 0, verify queue has 2 items and editingIndex is now 1.
5. `removeFromQueue when editing the removed item resets editingIndex to null` ‚Äî add 2 items, start editing index 0, remove index 0, verify editingIndex is null.
6. `removeFromQueue when editing item after removed one decrements editingIndex` ‚Äî add 3 items, start editing index 2, remove index 1, verify editingIndex is 1.
7. `startEditing sets editingIndex and returns content` ‚Äî add item with content 'test', call startEditing(0), verify return value is 'test' and editingIndex is 0.
8. `cancelEditing resets editingIndex to null` ‚Äî startEditing, then cancelEditing, verify editingIndex is null.
9. `saveEditing updates item content and resets editingIndex` ‚Äî add item, startEditing(0), saveEditing('updated'), verify queue[0].content is 'updated' and editingIndex is null.
10. `auto-flush fires on streaming to idle transition` ‚Äî render with status 'streaming', add an item to queue, then rerender with status 'idle', verify onFlush was called with annotated content.
11. `auto-flush prepends timing annotation to flushed content` ‚Äî verify the flushed string starts with '[Note: This message was composed while the agent was responding to the previous message]'.
12. `auto-flush skips when sessionBusy is true` ‚Äî render with status 'streaming' and sessionBusy true, add item, transition to idle, verify onFlush not called.
13. `auto-flush skips the item being edited` ‚Äî add 2 items, start editing index 0, transition streaming to idle, verify onFlush is called with the second item's content (index 1).
14. `auto-flush does nothing when queue is empty` ‚Äî transition streaming to idle with empty queue, verify onFlush not called.
15. `queue clears on sessionId change` ‚Äî add items, rerender with different sessionId, verify queue is empty.
16. `queue clears on selectedCwd change` ‚Äî add items, rerender with different cwd, verify queue is empty.

## Acceptance Criteria

